overview: Zoom (33) is at war with herself. Zoom wants to do normal things - go on dates, go to clubs, stay fit, but her anxious mind thwarts her efforts at every opportunity, and everything she tries to do just seems to take a little bit longer. Me, Myself, vs. I follows the three personalities Zoom possesses, as she struggles with her disordered relationship with anxiety.
title: Me, Myself, vs. I
